 《BattleBit Remastered》即将登陆 Steam Deck https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/battlebit-remastered-is-coming-to-steam-deck-3469394?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=battlebit-remastered-is-coming-to-steam-甲板Imogen DonovanMon, 17 Jul 2023 11:46:03 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPC https://www.nme.com/?p=3469394 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/battlebit-remastered-steam-deck-compatibility.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/battlebit-remastered-steam-deck-compatibility.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/battlebit-remastered-steam-deck-compatibility-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/battlebit-remastered-steam-deck-compatibility-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/battlebit-remastered-steam-deck-compatibility-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/battlebit-remastered-steam-deck-compatibility-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/battlebit-remastered-steam-deck-compatibility-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>团队只有三名开发人员</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/battlebit-remastered-is-coming-to-steam-deck-3469394">《BattleBit Remastered》即将登陆 Steam Deck 的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/battlebit-remastered-steam-deck-compatibility.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/battlebit-remastered-steam-deck-compatibility.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/battlebit-remastered-steam-deck-compatibility-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/battlebit-remastered-steam-deck-compatibility-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/battlebit-remastered-steam-deck-compatibility-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/battlebit-remastered-steam-deck-compatibility-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/battlebit-remastered-steam-deck-compatibility-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/battlebit-remastered"><em>《BattleBit Remastered》</em></a>即将登陆<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/steam">Steam</a> Deck，因此很快就会让数以万计的玩家随时随地畅玩游戏。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/why-steam-next-fests-demos-are-a-vital-celebration-of-gamings-future-3459650">为什么 Steam Next Fest 的演示是对游戏未来的重要庆祝</a></strong></li></ul><p>正如游戏官方<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/discord">Discord</a>服务器（通过<em><a href="https://steamdeckhq.com/news/battlebit-remastered-steam-deck-support/">SteamDeckHQ</a></em> ）所宣布的那样，电子竞技系统和反作弊软件 FACEIT 正在推出支持<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/linux">Linux</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/steam-deck">Steam Deck</a>的新版本。 <em>《BattleBit Remastered》</em>将是第一款在该版本上运行的游戏，据说它是比前身“更休闲的版本”，尽管目前还不清楚这意味着什么。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="BattleBit 重制版 - 官方预告片" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/DCLDlKFkc3Y?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>双方均未说明新版 FACEIT 的预计时间或游戏登陆 Steam Deck 的预计时间。尽管如此， <em>《BattleBit Remastered》</em>仍然在 Steam 上获得了大量关注，并因其内容的经济性而受到好评。</p><p> <em>BattleBit Remastered</em>售价 15 美元（12.79 英镑），支持 254 个玩家服务器，并为玩家在超过 19 个多人游戏地图上进行近距离语音聊天。与<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/battlefield"><em>《战地》</em></a>一样，竞技场也具有高度可破坏性，社区热烈欢迎<em>《BattleBit Remastered》</em> ，因为它为玩家提供了预算有限的一切。</p><p>展望未来， <em>《BattleBit Remastered》</em>的玩家将期待“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/battlebit-remastered-outlines-bright-future-after-overwhelming-launch-3463968">新武器、小工具、地图以及现有地图的重制版</a>”，开发商正计划招募一支内部反作弊团队。</p><p> <em>《BattleBit Remastered》</em>由三人团队历时六年打造而成，是 2023 年的成功故事之一，在 Steam 上发布后两周内就售出了 180 万份。从那时起， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/battlefield-style-shooter-battlebit-remastered-takes-steam-by-storm-3459570">玩家人数峰值</a>已达到 87,000 人，截至撰写本文时，游戏中的玩家人数约为 30,000 人，“超出了[开发者]的预期。”</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/fable-narrative-lead-anna-megill-leaves-playground-games-3469308">安娜·梅吉尔</a>将离开<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/brands/playground-games">Playground Games</a> 。 《<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/games/fable"><em>神鬼</em></a>寓言》的叙事负责人表示，这个选择并不容易，她在即将推出的角色扮演游戏中的经历是“梦想成真”。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/battlebit-remastered-is-coming-to-steam-deck-3469394">《BattleBit Remastered》即将登陆 Steam Deck 的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
玛丽娜畅谈健康斗争：“很难记住健康的感觉” https://www.nme.com/news/music/marina-opens-up-about-health-struggles-its-been-hard-to-remember-what-healthy-feels-like-3469406?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=码头开放有关健康的斗争，很难记住健康的感觉Liberty DunworthMon, 17 Jul 2023 11:12:37 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3469406 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marina@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Marina 在 2022 年温伍德骄傲节第二天登台表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marina@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marina@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marina@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marina@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marina@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marina@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位歌手最近被诊断出患有慢性疲劳综合症</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marina-opens-up-about-health-struggles-its-been-hard-to-remember-what-healthy-feels-like-3469406">玛丽娜 (Marina) 公开谈论健康问题：“很难记住健康的感觉”，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marina@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Marina 在 2022 年温伍德骄傲节第二天登台表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marina@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marina@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marina@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marina@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marina@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marina@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/marina">玛丽娜·迪亚曼迪斯 (Marina Diamandis)</a>分享了她持续的健康斗争和最近诊断出的慢性疲劳综合症的见解。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/marina-interview-ancient-dreams-modern-land-2973113">我们从与玛丽娜的对话视频聊天中学到的五件事</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位以玛丽娜为艺名的流行歌星在社交媒体上向歌迷讲述了她正在进行的健康斗争，并详细介绍了她在过去七年中所面临的症状。</p><p>她还透露，近几个月来，她被诊断出患有慢性疲劳综合症，这种长期病症会使人缺乏精力，无法进行日常活动。</p><p>在上周（7 月 12 日）分享到 Instagram 的帖子中，这位歌手向歌迷回忆了“深度疲劳、麻木、刺痛、脑雾、皮疹、失眠和一种‘中毒’的感觉等症状”，并表示她长期以来，她一直在与这些问题作斗争，以至于“很难记住健康是什么感觉”。</p><p> “很长一段时间以来，我的基线能量一直保持在 50% 至 60%。除了几次缓解期之外，过去 7 年里我每天都是依靠肾上腺素和意志力度过的，”她补充道。</p><p> “经过大量研究，我现在了解到这些症状是由于慢性压力而产生的过敏性神经系统的结果。 ⁣我的身体感觉陷入了‘战斗或逃跑’模式，在最严重的症状出现之前，它给了我很多警告信号。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CunFXHrPoJB/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xl